highlights.text: Tu Aake Dekhle by King has been on Top Songs Ahmedabad the longest, at 66 weeks straight.
TERE TE by AP Dhillon and Gurinder Gill is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Ahmedabad, up 44 spots at #51.
Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Ahmedabad. Kesariya is the highest at #3.
Jhoome Jo Pathaan - Arabic Version by Vishal-Shekhar, Grini, Jamila El Badaoui, Kumaar, and Jalal Hamdaoui is the highest new entry on Top Songs Ahmedabad at #37.
